{"word":"H6119 - עָקֵב - ʻâqêb - aw-kabe' - Heel","slug":"H6119","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָקֵב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâqêb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-kabe'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Heel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05E7;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05E7;&#x05D1; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;qe&#x0302;b  &#x201B;iqq<sup>e</sup>ba&#x0302;h</b> - <i>aw-kabe', ik-keb-aw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6117\">H6117</a>; a <i>heel</i> (as <i>protuberant</i>); hence a <i>track</i>; figuratively the <i>rear</i> (of an army). (<i>lier in wait</i> is by mistake for <a href=\"#/H6120\">H6120</a>.): - heel, [horse-] hoof, last, lier in wait [by mistake for <a href=\"#/H6120\">H6120</a>], (foot-) step."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3290\">H3290</a>, <a href=\"#/H3291\">H3291</a>, <a href=\"#/H6117\">H6117</a>, <a href=\"#/H6118\">H6118</a>, <a href=\"#/H6120\">H6120</a>, <a href=\"#/H6121\">H6121</a>, <a href=\"#/H6122\">H6122</a>, <a href=\"#/H6126\">H6126</a>"}]}